https://match.grew.fr/

# Negation-related Croft Constructions

# German:
# Negation particle "nicht"

pattern{
Neg[form="nicht"]
}

# Neg-word
pattern{
Neg[lemma="niemand"|"nichts"|"nirgends"|"kein"|"nirgendwo"]
}

pattern{
V[upos="VERB"];
Neg[lemma="niemand"|"nichts"|"nirgends"|"kein"|"nirgendwo"];
Subj[];
V-[nsubj]->Subj;
V->Neg
}

# English:
# Negative clauses in English according to Huddleston & Pullum

Verbal negation:
Negation particle following an auxililary

Non-verbal negation:
Neg-word: 
